# Spot the Difference Game

A simple and fun **Spot the Difference** game built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
Find all the differences between two images within a set time limit!

---

## Features

- Selectable time limit (30, 60, 90, 120 seconds)
- Visual markers highlight found differences
- Score tracking with star ratings
- Win or time-up message with restart option
- Responsive design for desktop and mobile
- Sound effect on finding a difference

---

## How to Play

1. Select the time limit from the dropdown menu.
2. Click **Start Game** to begin.
3. Spot all the differences by clicking on the images.
4. Find all differences before time runs out to win!
5. Restart the game anytime from the win/time-up screen.

